high_descs: Turn around and step forward to face the cabinet below the microwave.
Pick up the plate in the cabinet below the microwave.
Turn around and step forward to face the fridge.
Cool the plate in the fridge and remove it.
Turn left and walk forward to face the sink.
Place the plate in the sink.
anns.task_desc: To cool a plate plus place it in the sink.

high_descs: Turn right and go to the microwave.
Pick up the plate from the cabinet below the microwave.
Turn around and go to the fridge.
Chill the plate in the fridge and pick it back up.
Turn to the left and go to the sink.
Put the plate in the sink.
anns.task_desc: Put a chilled plate in the sink.

high_descs: Turn right and walk to the microwave on your right then turn right to face it and walk to it.
Open the cabinet under the microwaves left side and grab the plate that's under there then close the door.
Turn right and take two steps then turn right and walk to the fridge.
Chill the plate in the fridge then take it back out and close the door.
Turn left and take two steps to your left then walk forward to the sink.
Put the plate in the sink.
anns.task_desc: Put a cold plate in the sink.
